ari, Bikinis, and Games</h2>Exhausted from your travels? The Palm Paw Resort just opened up to those with sufficient coin! Take a load off and enlist your companions in a match of Kiss Kiss Volleyball or try your luck at Slots, Coin Toss, or Star Cards. A perfect get-away for hard working adventurers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256280/extras/bd9f93e6ef25832f8da39ac9d0516c92.poster.avif?t=1772171848\" width=576 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256280/extras/bd9f93e6ef25832f8da39ac9d0516c92.webm?t=1772171848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256280/extras/bd9f93e6ef25832f8da39ac9d0516c92.mp4?t=1772171848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A word from the developer...</h2>Not enough lady-meat in your RPGs?<br><br>Project Skyward is a love-letter to classic JRPGs and the futanari fandom. It is a story about an air-headed futa adventurer who is thrust into a realm at war. As an aspiring hero, you'll be expected to rise and meet the coming threat. All the quest-giving MILFs are counting on you after all...<br><br>Unsheathe your blade! <br>Journey to slay the evil Demon Queen Eraanthe.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256280/extras/61ceaf9775e91b9cb3ad7e85b49b29ca.avif?t=1772171848\" width=668 height=362 /></span>", "short_description": "A turn-based futanari rpg. Challenging dungeons, bosses, puzzles, romance quests, collectables, mini games, hentai scenes &amp; more!", "supported_languages": "English", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256280/5b1b7a90287add355ddd35931f7aafe311601d4a/header.jpg?t=1772171848", "capsule_image": "https:/